A style primarily and use base weaps for filler.  Ever notice on the Merc and BM reports how it is constantly stated how we use base weapon styles, CDW for filler?  You are*still*better off than us.  Ever notice how the majority of the CDW styles suck?  They really do.  Majority of them are just thrown together.  You don't realize the pain we've been through because of you.  I don't even know if you guys could bend over to tie your shoes because of the balance issues pre-1.62.  Post-1.62 you are still more viable to play than mercs or BMs.  No.  You don't have Flurry.  Yes, you still have better style damage.  No you can't spec in shield.  Yes, only .5 percent of the BM and merc population specs shield higher than 7.  You lose all parry and evade and half your AF for 20 seconds.  20 seconds.  Really, do you really evade and parry enough in twenty seconds that you sometimes refrain from Frenzy?  If so then you are still not in the same boat as Mercs and BMs.  I do not know if it's true or not, but I read somewhere on your board speccing LA gets you higher evade chance.  Glance over to Merc Ask TL, second page of 'Cath, are any of these going to be addressed?'  You'll notice that both BM and Zerker take significantly less damage than a mercenary over time.  If the LA=More Evade is true, you're damaged for even less than the Blademaster, making the Berserker even more defensive than Blademaster.  Ever notice how you get Avoid Pain?  We don't.  Probably never will.  So, you all take less damage than Mercs and BMs over time and you get Avoid Pain.  How can you really justify that?  Blademasters*need*TW.  Ever glance at Hippy Land styles as a whole?  Pierce is the only line that doesn't look like it was just thrown together.  So hm...all three weapon lines for you are worth speccing.  With mercs Slash is reasonably best, crush second and thrust only if you're Saracen.  But BMs....only one line is actually pretty nice?  How do you justify that?  Please tell me.  How is it you believe Mercenaries have a better class skill than you?  Dirty Tricks isn't that great.  It's a proc for one, so if you are really unlucky it won't fire at all.  A 35% proc that causes a 50% chance to fumble.  How is that better than critting every hit for 20 seconds?  Sure, you lose half your AF and no parry or evade.  But if you were actually playing your class how it should be played,  you woudln't have anything attacking you in the first place.  Oh in RvR you are getting slaughtered.  Play a mercenary or blademaster.  We get slaughtered to.  Y'know what's funny about Dirty Tricks and you guys? Even if Dirty Tricks does proc, your left hand will still hit and crit.  You get haste effect 100% of the time*and*your left hand always hits.  Hmm...and you say we'll do more damage over time than you?  Unstyled?  Style?  Please, let us see the logs.  No.  You are not worse off than we are.  You are a light tank.  You shouldn't take down pure tanks.  Period.<br>
<br>
Again, I am not trying to stir up any trouble whatsoever.  I am sorry that you were brought down to your rightful level so abrubtly.  But you all need to realize that you are pissing and moaning about something that should have been done a long time ago.<br>
<br>
I wish all of you luck on learning your newly realized tole as light tanks.  May you all learn to love the light tank class like all of the diehard Mercenaries and Blademasters that post on these boards.<br>
<br>
Peace,<br>
Joe<br>
<br>
P.S.  Mythic doesn't lie and cheat.  They do everything for a reason.  They are not stupid.  They can't do everything because other classes have issues too.  So shut up about how much you hate Mythic.  Wanna hate a company?  Play EQ and hate Verant.  They deserve it at least.<br>
